                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">woman</span> Dames
                    </h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                            <span>Knippen & Drogen</span>
                            <span class="font-bold">v.a. € 25,00</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                            <span>Knippen & Föhnen</span>
                            <span class="font-bold">v.a. € 31,00</span>
